{
  "stem": "2906.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But when we came out from Poland, and we had to go there on hills, the Polish people, whatever anybody have something, they took away.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They got a ring, or you got anything-- we didn't have much.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They cleaned us out-- everything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But in Czechoslovakia, the people are so nice.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I still remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were very nice to us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we stayed there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They gave us food.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They took sick people to the hospital.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And from there, we had to go to-- [SIGHS] to-- they took us to Austria.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "In Austria, to-- we came to Salzburg.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And in--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was the DP camps.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Salzburg gave out DP camps.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they took us to the DP camps, which the American took care of us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, we stayed there for a while.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A DP camp is just like a-- they have little places were to sleep, and they give you something to eat.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and there was a director.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She was from the United-- from from America.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But she she steal all the-- the food what they were supposed to give us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they didn't give us much what to eat.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we always ran out of, you know-- there was nothing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You-- you-- they give you a little bit of water or something to-- it wasn't-- it wasn't good.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they find out-- nothing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was nothing to do.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So, my husband find out that in Hallein is a new DP, and they need policemen.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So a lot of the boys, they went to Hallein, and they--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By Salzburg.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This what I have the-- and-- and then, I came there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We stayed there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My daughter was born there in 1947.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My husband, he was very intelligent, and a very nice man.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
